\id 2JN Reconstructed from Ventura Publisher
\h 2 Zon
\toc1 Khe Zon Phenat…®t…®gap Khergi Gap
\toc2 2 Zon
\toc3 2 Zo
\mt1 2 ZON
\mt2 Khe Zon Phenat…®t…®gap Khergi Gap
\imt1 Khe fharav gan…®nga buni khare.
\ip Khe Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi gari guman pana mbe khergi gap khare. Gumgi vh…®rve mbe kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui, ana kha gava khergiap, sios mbe ndi mbarigi. Ana khueŇč vuzvugi, mbe wari won ndavir harigi nt…®…®ri n…®…®Ňčv, t…®var vhuun mben muuŇčri. Mbe vh…®ra mba bigi guiguigi gumgi, mbe tuituigip mbe gan…®ri, Fhe Bak…®me bunin vhuuiŇč, mbe nta domdora suav, nta nzuai gumgi ma. Nza guigira Fhe Bak…®me buni guari, nza guigira ntan suirav havhargirga. Nza ntan suirav havhargip, nza tuituigira harigi buni bun nzuai gumgi, nza mbe buni mbarararga.
\c 1
\ms1 Nza KhaŇč T…®g…® Havhargip Fhe Bak…®men Buna VhuueŇč Suira Havhargip, Tuituigira Mba Harigi Khesharigi Buni Bun Nzuai Gumgi Gan…®ri.
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt Zo 8.32; 1 Pi 5.1; 1 Zo 3.18; 3 Zo 1.1\x*Gu Zisas khoth…®gap, ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi gari guman pan, gu kha gava khergiap, ndu Fhe Bak…®me won mbuigi mbik, ndu won tari kov, gu nde ndi mbai. Gu guigira khar nzuai, gu guigira wo ndavar nde n…®…®Ňčgi. Gu nduara won ndavar nde n…®…®Ňčgi fhuvara. Kha buni guari kaŇčgi gumgi gu mbigi, mbe zam guigira wari won ndavir nde n…®…®Ňčgi. \f a \fr 1:1 \ft Gumgi mbari kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui, kha gap, ana guigira mbiga guara ndi khergi. Mbe mbari kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui, mba mbik ana sios mbe ma, ana mba siosan ki gumgi gu mbigi ma. Ana maaŇč muuŇčgi sios thevi, ana phorge r…®gi mbiga h…®r…®…®Ňč, ana nzuai kameŇč ves 13 ki. Mba ves, ana bun nzuai, ana vh…®ra sios mbe ma. \f*
\v 2 Kha buni guari nta nzan ki. Mba buni nta zazera mbara muuŇčgip nzan k…®rga. Nza maaŇč muuŇčgiap nza guigira wari won ndavir nde n…®…®Ňčgi.
\v 3 Nza kha buni guari z…®n vui t…®v gum nza guigira ndavir harigi nt…®…®ri ga nd…®…®i t…®v, Fhe Bak…®me gum Zisas Krais, ana Fhe Bak…®men Kam, mani fhura nzan kora mbuav, nzan kurkurigi t…®v gum manin ndava m…®…®t…®k, guigira khaŇč t…®g…®p havhargip nza ndavi vherir k…®v, k…®rar h…®ri.
\s1 Nza guigira wari won ndavir harigi gumgi gu mbigi ga nd…®…®i t…®va z…®n Ňčg…®ri.
\p 
\v 4 \x - \xo 1:4 \xt 3 Zo 1.3\x*Gu ndun tari mbari mbararagim, mbe Fhe Bak…®me nza suaŇčgi t…®va z…®n vov, mbe buni guari z…®n vuim, gu ne mbararagiap, gu guigira ne nzuav ndikndigi.
\v 5 \x - \xo 1:5 \xt Zo 13.34; 15.12; 15.17; 1 Pi 4.8; 1 Zo 2.7-8; 3.11; 3.23\x*Ndu Fhe Bak…®me farasarigi mbik, gu buna mueŇč ndun ki. Gu khueŇč vuzvugi, nde mba buneŇč z…®n Ňčg…®ri. Mba buneŇč khare, nza guigira wari won ndavir zam harigi nt…®…®ri n…®…®nga. Gu khar t…®var kameŇč khergiap, ndu ndi mbav, ne z…®n Ňčg…®r zav ndu nzuai fhuvara. Nza fhum kha t…®va kaŇčgi.
\v 6 \x - \xo 1:6 \xt Zo 14.15; 14.21; 1 Zo 2.5; 2.24; 5.3\x*Guigira won ndavar harigi nt…®…®ri ga nd…®…®i t…®v, ana khaŇč muuŇčgi. Nza guigira Fhe Bak…®me suaŇčgi t…®vi z…®n vui. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nde fhum mbararagi t…®v khaŇč nzuai, nde guigira wari won ndavir harigi nt…®…®ri ga nd…®…®i t…®v, nde mba t…®va z…®n Ňčg…®ri.
\s1 Nza Krais buna vhuueŇč suira havhargiri.
\p 
\v 7 \x - \xo 1:7 \xt 1 Zo 2.22; 4.1-3\x*Nde mbarara, gumgi vh…®rve, mbe nza guiguigi zav, za kha nuiana rui. Mbe Zisas Krais kha nuianan zergap, guma guara gegi, mbe ne khoth…®gi fhu. MaaŇč nzuai gumgi, mbe bigi guiguigi gumgi ma, mbe vh…®ra Zisasan pana gumgi ma. \f b \fr 1:7 \ft Ndu 1 Zon 4.2 ki kameŇč gan…®ri. \f*
\v 8 \x - \xo 1:8 \xt Mk 10.29-30; Ga 3.4; Hi 10.32; 10.35\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nde tuituigia wari gan…®ri. Nde muuŇčv k…®v, nza mba Ňčaara mbat…®ga mbuav ndigi big…®n, ana fhura mbar Ňčg…®g…® rivgi. Nde khaŇč t…®g…®p th…®g…® havhargirga, nde za ana ndigirga.
\v 9 \x - \xo 1:9 \xt 1 Zo 2.23\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgip, guma the Krais buni suirav havhar…® thav, feg…®p harigi bunin mbarav, nta z…®n Ňčg…®rga, Fhe Bak…®me mba guma phorg…® keg…®rga tukt…®gi fhuvara. Guma Krais buni suirav havhargirga, Fhe Bak…®me won Kaman kov, mani mba guma phorga ki.
\v 10 \x - \xo 1:10 \xt Ef 5.11; 2 Te 3.6\x*Nde maaŇč muuŇčgip k…®rim, guma the nde han z…®v, ana Krais nza kh…®vigi buni ndiga nde han zi fhu, nde raar vhuun ana n…®…®Ňč thari, nde vh…®ra ana ndigip, wari wo phenin Ňčg…® thari.
\v 11 Guma mba khesharigi guma, ana raar vhuun ana nd…®…®i, ana anan Ňčaara mbat…®gar kurkurigi.
\s1 Guman pan mbe gan…®ngeŇč vuzvugi.
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 1:12 \xt Zo 17.13; 1 Zo 1.4; 3 Zo 1.13-14\x*Gu gavar buni vh…®rvera khergiap, nde ndi mbae, gu thagi, gu gavar mba buni kher…®rgeŇč thagi. Gu kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui, gu nduara Ňčg…®v, nde gan…®v, nza wari phorg…®p buni suaŇčv, nza guigira ndikndiga mbat…®gar muunga.
\p 
\v 13 Ndun mbiga h…®r…®…®Ňč, Fhe Bak…®me ana won mbuiav, ana farasarigi, anan tari raar vhuun ndu nd…®…®i. \f c \fr 1:13 \ft Ndu 2 Zon ves 1 ki kameŇč gan…®ri. \f*
